{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these guys would laugh at us when we made the-- this quorum, but a lot of them came along.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had there about 30 or 40 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was giving my cantorial rendition there with the knowledge that some guys are watching outside and that everything is safe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Except one of the guys was goofing off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the middle of my praying one of the SS walks in with a pistol in the hand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and he shoots out a bullet above my head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think he was aiming at me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, maybe because he knew me, I don't know why, but he yelled out loud and clear, what do you think this is, a cheder, like a Jewish school?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Disperse right away, or I'll kill all of you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So of course we all ran away, and we later on had to bawl that one guy out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it's like putting somebody on a-- on a mission to watch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, the guy could have really taken the gun and killed us all, and he would have not to report, to give an accounting for, to anybody.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So at worst that I can say, that in-- in the goodness of his heart, he didn't have a-- a heart to-- to kill us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm sure he could have-- he could have aimed at me and shoot me, and he purposely did it above my head.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I'm pretty sure at this point, because we never undertook another trial like this again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by that time, that was already getting to the end of the time where the-- where the guys who ran away from Auschwitz-- I must have read a book about this.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
